  <refnamediv>
    <refname>printfigure</refname>
    <refpurpose>Opens a printing dialog and prints a figure.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>
printfigure(figid)
status = printfigure(figid)
    </synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Arguments</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>figid</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>Real: the id of the figure to be printed.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>status</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>Boolean: <emphasis>%T</emphasis> if the printing succeeds, <emphasis>%F</emphasis> otherwise.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>This function opens a dialog to select a printer, printing options... and then prints the figure.</para>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Examples</title>
    <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[ 
plot2d();
printfigure(get(gcf(), "figure_id"));
 ]]></programlisting>
  </refsection>
